<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Trang chủ | Hệ thống Thuê xe Premium</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            /* Premium Color Palette */
            --bg-color: #0f172a;
            --surface-color: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);
            --surface-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            --primary-glow: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --card-hover: rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.8);

            /* Typography */
            --font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;

            /* Animations */
            --transition-smooth: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-family);
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(circle at 15% 50%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 85% 30%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Glassmorphism Header */
        .header {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
            padding: 1.2rem 4rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .header-logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .nav a {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav a:hover {
            color: var(--text-main);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .nav a.active {
            color: var(--text-main);
            background: var(--surface-border);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        /* Main Content */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
            border-radius: 9999px;
            color: #60a5fa;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .page-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .page-title span {
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .page-desc {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Cards Grid */
        .cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--surface-color);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            text-align: left;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        /* Glow effect on hover */
        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            opacity: 0;
            z-index: -1;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
            background: var(--card-hover);
            border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 0 20px var(--primary-glow);
        }

        .card-icon-wrap {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .card.cars .card-icon-wrap {
            color: #60a5fa;
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
        }

        .card.bookings .card-icon-wrap {
            color: #f472b6;
            background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.1);
        }

        .card:hover .card-icon-wrap {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .card-arrow {
            margin-top: auto;
            align-self: flex-start;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #8b5cf6;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .card:hover .card-arrow {
            gap: 1rem;
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* Custom Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header {
                padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .page-title {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header-logo">CarRental</div>
        <nav class="nav">
            <a href="/" class="active">Trang chủ</a>
            <a href="/views/cars">Danh sách xe</a>
            <a href="/views/bookings">Đặt xe</a>
            <a href="/views/overdue">Quá hạn</a>
            <span id="guestNav">
                <a href="/views/login">Đăng nhập</a>
                <a href="/views/register">Đăng ký</a>
            </span>
            <span id="userNav" style="display:none; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem;">
                <span style="font-size:0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 9999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);"><span id="userEmail" style="color: #60a5fa; font-weight: 600;"></span></span>
                <a href="#" id="indexLogout" style="padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 9999px; border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.4); background: rgba(239,68,68,0.15); color: #fca5a5; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none;">Đăng xuất</a>
            </span>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="hero-badge">Hệ thống quản lý v2.0</div>
        <h1 class="page-title">Trải nghiệm di chuyển<br><span>Hoàn hảo & Tiện lợi</span></h1>
        <p class="page-desc">Nền tảng quản lý thuê xe hiện đại. Tối ưu hóa vận hành, theo dõi trạng thái xe theo thời
            gian thực và quản lý các giao dịch đặt xe một cách dễ dàng.</p>

        <div class="cards">
            <a href="/views/cars" class="card cars">
                <div class="card-icon-wrap">🚘</div>
                <h3>Quản lý Garage</h3>
                <p>Khám phá bộ sưu tập xe đa dạng. Theo dõi thông số, tiện nghi và trạng thái sẵn sàng của toàn bộ
                    phương tiện trong hệ thống.</p>
                <div class="card-arrow">Xem danh sách <span>→</span></div>
            </a>

            <a href="/views/bookings" class="card bookings">
                <div class="card-icon-wrap">📋</div>
                <h3>Giao dịch Đặt xe</h3>
                <p>Tạo và theo dõi các hợp đồng thuê xe. Hệ thống tự động tính toán chi phí minh bạch dưa trên thời gian
                    sử dụng thực tế.</p>
                <div class="card-arrow">Quản lý đặt xe <span>→</span></div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>
    <script>
        (function () {
            var token = localStorage.getItem('token');
            var guestNav = document.getElementById('guestNav');
            var userNav = document.getElementById('userNav');
            var userEmail = document.getElementById('userEmail');
            if (token && userNav && guestNav) {
                guestNav.style.display = 'none';
                userNav.style.display = 'inline-flex';
                try {
                    var user = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('user') || '{}');
                    if (userEmail) userEmail.textContent = user.email || user.fullName || 'User';
                } catch (e) {}
            }
            var logoutBtn = document.getElementById('indexLogout');
            if (logoutBtn) {
                logoutBtn.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    localStorage.removeItem('token');
                    localStorage.removeItem('user');
                    window.location.reload();
                });
            }
        })();
    </script>
</body>

</html>